# Portfolio Web – Snezhana Pashovska (EN)

## 🇬🇧 Description
My personal portfolio is a website designed to present my recent projects and web development skills. It is built with **HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap**, and hosted on **GitHub Pages** for easy access.  

The site is currently **in French**, but an English version will be available soon to reach an international audience.

## 🌟 Current Status
The website is **finished and stable**. I am happy with its design and functionality. Minor updates may be made in the future to add new projects or improve the user experience.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap  
- **Design**: Pastel, minimalistic, feminine palette  
- **Hosting**: GitHub Pages  

## 📌 Main Features
- Showcase of recent projects via interactive cards  
- Functional contact form  
- Responsive and clean design  
- Smooth and intuitive navigation  

## 🔜 Upcoming Plans
- Full **English translation** of the website  
- Addition of new projects and UX improvements  

## 👩‍💻 Author
**Snezhana Zafar Pashovska**  

🌐 [Visit the live site](https://snezhanapashovska.github.io/portfolio/)
